document.title: NI 43-101 Technical Report for the Thierry Project in North America dated June 2012.pdf
document.description: This technical report provides an independent National Instrument 43-101 compliant preliminary economic assessment of the Thierry and K1-1 Cu-Ni-PGE deposits in North-Western Ontario, evaluating both underground and open pit mining operations.
